Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ザァーー（雨音）\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待ってろよ　今日こそ　俺が…。\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・ザザザザザ…\Nん？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ザザザザザ…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出たな　悪魔め！\Nお前は…　お前は→\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俺が　倒す!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,バシャーン！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
